  undeadType: 6
  habitat: Vaettir Habitat
  description: The Vaettir is a creature that lives closer to humans than any other
    creature.  It is fairly small, and they live underneath stables, fireplaces or
    even underground passages. Humans that are kind enough to help the Vaettir, can
    be rewarded.   But be wary, the Vaettir can also be vengeful, spreading diseases
    or burning down the farm.
